- Yeah, that's really,
really powerful.

00:26:52.560 --> 00:26:53.580
Thanks for coming, Ben.

00:26:56.460 --> 00:26:58.710
What do you see the
Lord doing through you,

00:26:58.710 --> 00:26:59.730
where you are today?

00:26:59.730 --> 00:27:02.670
You're still next to Pete
and all these guys who

00:27:02.670 --> 00:27:04.560
are so far in their career.

00:27:04.560 --> 00:27:07.740
And how do you see him
nudging you and using you

00:27:07.740 --> 00:27:09.130
where you are today?

00:27:09.130 --> 00:27:10.300
BEN MALCOLMSON: Yeah,
that's a great question.

00:27:10.300 --> 00:27:12.630
And I think what
this story has taught

00:27:12.630 --> 00:27:15.930
me all along is
that we often don't

00:27:15.930 --> 00:27:19.350
see the fruit of our
labor in the moment.

00:27:19.350 --> 00:27:21.240
Like that story, it
took me four years later

00:27:21.240 --> 00:27:24.460
to see what God was
doing all along.

00:27:24.460 --> 00:27:25.800
And so I feel that today.

00:27:25.800 --> 00:27:27.290
I still feel discouraged today.

00:27:27.290 --> 00:27:30.270
Man, like, do I have a purpose
in the spot that I'm in?

00:27:30.270 --> 00:27:32.700
And so I'm just trusting and
knowing and just hopefully

00:27:32.700 --> 00:27:35.558
following the nudge every day
that God is placing me there

00:27:35.558 --> 00:27:36.100
for a reason.

00:27:36.100 --> 00:27:38.490
And I might not see the results.

00:27:38.490 --> 00:27:40.260
Just like many of you
in here, maybe you

00:27:40.260 --> 00:27:42.690
don't see the results
right now to why

00:27:42.690 --> 00:27:44.740
God has you where you're at.

00:27:44.740 --> 00:27:47.010
But just to know, and to
trust that God is working.

00:27:47.010 --> 00:27:49.130
And so I feel that every day.

00:27:49.130 --> 00:27:50.310
I wrestle every day.

00:27:50.310 --> 00:27:52.620
Like, do I listen
to discouragement,

00:27:52.620 --> 00:27:55.380
or do I listen to
the truth of God

00:27:55.380 --> 00:27:56.550
that he does have a purpose?

00:27:56.550 --> 00:27:59.640
And maybe someday down
the road, or when we all

00:27:59.640 --> 00:28:01.500
get to heaven some
day, we'll get

00:28:01.500 --> 00:28:03.720
to see what God was
doing all along.

00:28:03.720 --> 00:28:05.720
So thanks for that question.

00:28:05.720 --> 00:28:08.280
- So when you're
the butt of a prank,

00:28:08.280 --> 00:28:10.630
like I can so see
that happening.

00:28:10.630 --> 00:28:14.050
Because from what
little I know, I

00:28:14.050 --> 00:28:15.970
know there's a lot of pranking.

00:28:15.970 --> 00:28:19.240
And so what do you suggest
is the best mindset going

00:28:19.240 --> 00:28:21.460
into a prank?

00:28:21.460 --> 00:28:24.580
- To not take yourself
too seriously.

00:28:24.580 --> 00:28:27.890
I think a lot of times, we can
take ourselves way too serious.

00:28:27.890 --> 00:28:30.280
But that's the great
thing about Coach Carroll

00:28:30.280 --> 00:28:33.730
is that he's always keeping
things light and fun.

00:28:33.730 --> 00:28:36.350
And I think that's
what it's all about.

00:28:36.350 --> 00:28:38.237
So that's a great
question though.

00:28:38.237 --> 00:28:40.070
And hopefully, the
prank's not coming to me.

00:28:40.070 --> 00:28:41.740
I hope he doesn't tell
me 12 years later that it

00:28:41.740 --> 00:28:42.620
was all a joke.

00:28:42.620 --> 00:28:48.380
So thank you for that question.

00:28:48.380 --> 00:28:48.880
Awesome.

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:50.020
Well, thank you all so much.

00:28:50.020 --> 00:28:50.978
I appreciate your time.

00:28:50.978 --> 00:28:55.540
And if that story impacted
you, the book just

00:28:55.540 --> 00:28:58.360
came out a few months ago,
and it captures that story

00:28:58.360 --> 00:28:59.590
plus many other things.

00:28:59.590 --> 00:29:01.900
And whether you have a
friend who's into sports,

00:29:01.900 --> 00:29:03.280
or a young person
who's searching

00:29:03.280 --> 00:29:06.890
for their purpose, or maybe even
a friend or a family member,

00:29:06.890 --> 00:29:09.780
I think and I know that
this book will reach them

00:29:09.780 --> 00:29:11.070
in a really special way.

00:29:11.070 --> 00:29:12.820
So I hope you get a
chance to pick one up.

00:29:12.820 --> 00:29:13.918
Thank you.

00:29:13.918 --> 00:29:14.460
Thanks, Phil.

00:29:14.460 --> 00:29:15.043
Thank you all.

